<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_85" id="41v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_85_r1l16">Der Stat ʒu kempnicʒ </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_85_r1l17"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> habt </del> vnd <expan>gebett<ex>en</ex></expan> habt . von <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> frıcʒko <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l18">ʒu reden mıt <expan>etlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> vnd auch geſten / den er ſchuldıg ıſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l19">Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l20"><expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd auch geſt als vıl Jr auf dıſʒ ʒeıt bey vns anheim was . beſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l21">vnd fleıſſıg mıt Jn <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt . Dıe <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> / Daʒ ſıe dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l22"><expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> frıcʒko <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein geleyt <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> frawen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l23">tag lıechtmeſſ ſchıerıſt fur ſıe vnd dıe Jren on geuerd / Vnd beweıſe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l24">er ſıch in <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ʒeıt alſo <expan>geg<ex>en</ex></expan> Jn da mıt ſı <expan>Jr<ex>er</ex></expan> ſchulde von Jm ge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l25">trawen becʒalt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> bedurff er denn darauf <expan>leng<ex>er</ex>s</expan> geleyts von Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l26">da <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſıe <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> freẅntlıch ʒu <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l27">lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_85" id="41v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat zu Kempnicz</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>gebett<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        habt von <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Friczko <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        zu reden mit <expan>etliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> und auch gesten, den er schuldig ist etc.,
                        das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und auch gest, als vil ir auf disz zeit bey
                        uns anheim was, besant und fleissig mit in <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        geredt. Die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>, daz sie dem
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Friczko <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein
                        geleyt <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan><app>
<note><q type="date">
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frawentag liechtmess
                                schierist</q>02.02.1420</note>
</app> fur sie und die iren on geverd. Und beweise er sich in
                                <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> zeit also
                            <expan>geg<ex>en</ex></expan> in, da mit si <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        schulde von im getrawen beczalt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, bedurff er
                        denn darauf <expan>leng<ex>er</ex>s</expan> geleyts von in, da
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sie <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        frewntlich zu <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
